Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把房間弄得光亮些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後離我遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在對可惠隊長  敬禮!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早怎麼這麼吵?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可惠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她要外出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在交代警備的事務
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 可惠要出門去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(350,390)}『可惠的鍛煉』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上山狩獵?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,每年這個時候我都會出去修練
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是平常的鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓自己的技術退步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大自然裏面也可以鍛煉身心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒那麼棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有守衛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不一定每次都可以保護
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了預防萬一太郎大人也必須接受鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請馬上去做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃? 啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請保重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何? 太郎大人你來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這大自然的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們該下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼?!......
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先...先潔淨身體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果身心無法合一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會輸給瀑布的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身心合一...  身心合一...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是可惠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很鎮定的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你沒事吧,太郎大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是流木或者是什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,有我在你身邊  卻...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為從來沒做過  所以沒法做的好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人的腰力不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手腕和腰力要一致
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳步要站穩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰部放低一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再用力拉繩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個連貫動作要做的更加順暢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:05:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來作一次給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請仔細看著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣  這樣!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(是栗子!)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...我太激動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰部再用力些!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拳頭揮出去的瞬間用力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要像這樣子,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人,不是這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏要用點腰力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惠,你的胸部...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的肩膀上面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部  胸部  胸部...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上準備晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近會有什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香魚或者鱔魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些魚都是很難釣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就不要用釣的那麼麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你會用這種方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候和朋友都是這樣抓魚的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要對準大石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力的丟過去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是引起突發的震動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那些魚昏過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對,這麼大就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了嗎,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太...太郎大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我太興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何,和平時在庭園跑相比跑山路很累吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離目的地還很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是山野兔  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 還有一隻嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50}救命啊!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉,有我在你身邊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何? 還能跑嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想讓太郎大人看這幅景色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有一個姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個非常厲害  非常棒的一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:10:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我除了對她的敬仰  還有以她作為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會開始在這裏進行修練的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這種修練辛苦的讓人喘不過氣來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過每次看到這夕陽   一切的辛苦都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人  你做的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天讓你強壯了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在休息之前先去流些汗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近有個天然溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服  真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這溫泉真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫度剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  傷口會痛嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦? 健康男人的生理現象...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?  怎麼了,太郎大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的樣子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼說...這是沒辦法的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先離開一下或許...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你在身心方面的修練還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人和可惠呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是去接他們嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,聽說他們好像還要再繼續修練一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在太郎大人還沒有得到健全的身心前...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想回家!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖這麼說...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因都是可惠你啊～～!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓主人受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓主人遇到危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓主人...思春了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人,好合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第15話『依良的經驗』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回也要好好的聽主人差遣
